---

---

<section id="about" class="section about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Background</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="about-lead">
          I work across the full stack — from training AI models to shipping pixel-perfect
          interfaces. What drives me is the intersection of precision and possibility: building
          things that work beautifully and feel inevitable.
        </p>
        <p>
          With experience spanning software engineering, AI/ML, front-end architecture, and UI/UX
          design, I bring a cross-disciplinary perspective to every project. I care deeply about
          how things are built, how they feel to use, and how they hold up under real conditions.
        </p>
        <p>
          Outside of code, I'm interested in design systems, interaction design, typography, and
          the craft of making complex things feel simple.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-facts">
      <h3 class="facts-heading">Quick facts</h3>
      <dl class="facts-list">
        <div class="fact">
          <dt class="fact-label">Focus</dt>
          <dd class="fact-value">AI, Front-end, UI/UX</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <dt class="fact-label">Stack</dt>
          <dd class="fact-value">TypeScript, Python, React, Node</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <dt class="fact-label">Approach</dt>
          <dd class="fact-value">Precision-driven, human-centered</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <dt class="fact-label">Location</dt>
          <dd class="fact-value">Remote / Worldwide</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-inner {
    max-width: 80rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-xl);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink-subtle);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-facts {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid oklch(1 0 0 / 0.04);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .facts-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .facts-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .fact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .fact-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .fact-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
